#. translators: an annotation to a gpg keys expiry date
#: zypp-logic/zypp-common/PublicKey.cc:65
msgid "does not expire"
msgstr "δεν λήγει"

#. translators: an annotation to a gpg keys expiry date: "expired: 1999-04-12"
